<p>原创 吴栋 SCOP </p>
<p><img height="165" width="1080" src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201211/cd87be6d55f34da6b70f348cdc7109de.jpeg" /></p>
<p><img height="822" width="1080" src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201211/f51207bf62d042309347b88d4954f5ff.jpeg" /></p>
<p>Fork, 1928 </p>
<p>© André Kertész </p>
<p><img height="466" width="1080" src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201211/7222edb7ef254e69a563878889fff883.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
